---
title: Chipotle Spiced Sweet Potato and Bean Soup with Sweetcorn, Soured Cream and Tortilla Dippers
description: Our Chipotle Spiced Sweet Potato and Bean Soup is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
